A roller coaster simulator. Use points from data.txt to create 
a real time render roller coaster. The curves of the roller coaster
is Bezier curve that calculated from B-spline curve. and then 
subdivide the curves to smoothing the curves.

Hotkeys:
R: Start riding the roller coaster
S: Surround view of the roller coaster
P: Different render view of the roller coaster (Normal/Dots/Framework)

Notice:
change the opengl link library to own perfrom when compile the program.
Ex. on windows using freeglut:  -lfreeglut -lopengl32 -lglu32
